data.text: Thiruvisaipa & Thirupallandu are parts of Saiva Tirumuraiwhichare centuries-old hymns and songs on lord shiva Thiruvisaipatheninth volumes of the Tirumurai, the twelve-volume collectionofTamil Saivite devotional poetry.
